CONTENT: I have a job for you. It's a high-profile one. A journalist by the name of AZ. We need to silence them. They’ve been digging too deep into things that are better left alone. Are you interested?
Not sure, admin. You know I don't usually take jobs involving journalists. They tend to have too many connections. Why this one?

AZ has been publishing reports on things that could get *a lot* of people hurt. I've been monitoring their work for months now. They’re too close to a story that could compromise us all. It's getting worse.
I get it, but I need more details. Who is this AZ, and where do I find them?

AZ is a freelance journalist, late 30s. They’ve been on the radar for some time now, but recently started working on a series that could expose some of our contacts. I have their full dossier. The location is a house in the suburbs of New York. It's isolated, quiet.
I don’t like it. Journalists have a way of sniffing out danger. This could backfire. What exactly are they working on?

It’s a series on a corrupt government contract. The people involved are high profile. AZ is getting closer to tying everything together. If they publish what they know, it could ruin everything we've built.
Alright, I’ll take the job. But I’ll need a 20% increase in payment. This one feels... messy.
Done. You'll have the payment upfront, in full. Just make sure the job is clean.
Understood. I’ll start preparing. I’ll need a couple of days to get into position.
I'm in position. The target is still in their residence. No major changes in the schedule yet. I’ll be watching.
Any updates? It’s been a while, and AZ is still publishing. We need to move before they get any more attention.
I’ve been keeping my distance, but I’m seeing more security around the house. They’re aware they’re being watched. I’m not sure how long they’ll stay there.
I made contact. AZ knows something’s off. They're paranoid, got some new tech. They've gone into hiding.
What do you mean, ‘hiding’? This wasn’t part of the plan.
I’m telling you, they’re gone. I don’t know how, but they’ve found out about the job. They’ve pulled every single security measure. They're out of reach for now.
How sure are you? AZ can’t just vanish like that.
I’m sure. They’ve erased everything. Whoever is helping them is good. They’ve gone underground.
We need to know where they are. Find them, no matter what it takes.
I’ve found them. AZ is hiding in a safe at -8.064573212336882, -34.87379971789414. They’re using an encrypted connection to send out their reports. It’s secure. But I have their location.
Good. You know what to do. Finish it. TAC{help-is-on-the-way:063c3a20c004fea3108933d2617b64810f47293c786a9202df2714841569740e}
